        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "From Schubert’s Romantic Vision to Gershwin’s Jazz Inspired Fantasy. The Bergmann Duo is delighted to present Fantasies for Two, a richly expressive program celebrating the artistry and magic of piano four-hands performance."
